e":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The 5.5M goal was simple, stable, measurable, and fully actionable by the team, while still capturing an outcome that was useful for the business. Having more than six months of stability meant minimal disruption while we focused on this goal. By not being opinionated about implementation details, it drove many improvements in efficiency and performance across our backend systems, with trickle-down benefits to Enterprise deployments. However…","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":3784},"end":{"line":26,"column":447,"offset":4230}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":3784},"end":{"line":26,"column":447,"offset":4230}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"Long-standing-goals-may-have-diminishing-returns-over-time","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#Long-standing-goals-may-have-diminishing-returns-over-time","aria-label":"Long standing goals may have diminishing returns over time permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"Long-standing goals may have diminishing returns over time","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":5,"offset":4236},"end":{"line":28,"column":63,"offset":4294}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":4232},"end":{"line":28,"column":63,"offset":4294}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Past the 2M mark (six stars or more), our work was no longer generating trickle-down benefits for self-hosted customers. OSS search use cases on popular code were already well serviced. Reaching the 5.5M was not going to enable users to “search everything,” because 0-1 star repositories would not be included.","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1,"offset":4296},"end":{"line":30,"column":311,"offset":4606}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1,"offset":4296},"end":{"line":30,"column":311,"offset":4606}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"As a team, we challenged our continued focus on this goal. Was it still worth the significant, continued investment?","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1,"offset":4608},"end":{"line":32,"column":117,"offset":4724}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1,"offset":4608},"end":{"line":32,"column":117,"offset":4724}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"A-revised-goal-may-better-capture-the-desired-business-outcome","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#A-revised-goal-may-better-capture-the-desired-business-outcome","aria-label":"A revised goal may better capture the desired business outcome permalink","class":"anchor before"},"children":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 18 95 120\" height=\"18\" width=\"18\"><path d=\"M53.69,78.7H37.94l-5.85,25H21.74l5.85-25H15.89L18,69.1H29.84l4.65-19.65H23.39l2.1-9.6H36.74l5.7-23.7H52.79l-5.7,23.7H62.84l5.7-23.7H78.89l-5.7,23.7H84.74l-2.4,9.6H70.94L66.29,69.1H77.24l-2.4,9.6H64l-5.85,25H47.84Zm-13.5-9.6H55.94l4.65-19.65H44.84Z\"/></svg>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"A revised goal may better capture the desired business outcome","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":5,"offset":4730},"end":{"line":34,"column":67,"offset":4792}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1,"offset":4726},"end":{"line":34,"column":67,"offset":4792}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We questioned the 5.5M goal in discussion with product and engineering stakeholders:","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1,"offset":4794},"end":{"line":36,"column":85,"offset":4878}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1,"offset":4794},"end":{"line":36,"column":85,"offset":4878}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What was the intended outcome of this goal?","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":3,"offset":4882},"end":{"line":38,"column":46,"offset":4925}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1,"offset":4880},"end":{"line":38,"column":46,"offset":4925}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was this goal still the best path forward to the intended outcome?","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":3,"offset":4928},"end":{"line":39,"column":69,"offset":4994}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1,"offset":4926},"end":{"line":39,"column":69,"offset":4994}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If not, what would a better goal be?","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":3,"offset":4997},"end":{"line":40,"column":39,"offset":5033}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1,"offset":4995},"end":{"line":40,"column":39,"offset":5033}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}],"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1,"offset":4880},"end":{"line":40,"column":39,"offset":5033}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We agreed that universality was about more than scale, and shifted our focus to indexing repositories globally from more code hosts. This focus better captures the intended outcome of universality and sends a powerful message: your code is discoverable regardless of where it is hosted!","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1,"offset":5035},"end":{"line":42,"column":287,"offset":5321}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1,"offset":5035},"end":{"line":42,"column":287,"offset":5321}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":43,"column":1,"offset":5322}}}}